\c 100
\s Ihubo lokubonga iN\nd kosi\nd*
\d Isihlabelelo sokudumisa
\p
\v 1 Hlabelelani iN\nd kosi\nd* ngokuthaba\x + Hlab. 95.1.\x*, mhlaba wonke\x + Hlab. 95.1.\x*.
\v 2 Ikhonzeni iN\nd kosi\nd* ngenjabulo, wozani phambi kwayo ngokuhlabela ngentokozo\x + Hlab. 2.11.\x*.
\v 3 Yazini ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* inguNkulunkulu. Yiyo eyasenzayo, njalo ayisithi\x + Hlab. 95.6. Hlab. 119.73. 138.8. Efe. 2.10.\x*: \add si\add*ngabantu bayo\x + Hez. 34.30,31. Hlab. 74.1.\x* lezimvu zedlelo layo\x + Hez. 34.30,31. Hlab. 74.1.\x*.
\v 4 Ngenani emasangweni ayo ngokubonga\x + Hlab. 66.13.\x*, emagumeni ayo ngokudumisa\x + Hlab. 116.19.\x*. Ibongeni, lidumise ibizo layo.
\v 5 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ilungile\x + Hlab. 25.8. 34.8. 145.9. Nah. 1.7. 1 Lan. 16.34.\x*; umusa wayo \add uhlezi\add* kuze kube nininini\x + Hlab. 36.5.\x*, leqiniso layo esizukulwaneni lesizukulwana\x + Hlab. 36.5.\x*.